<h3 class="aboutHead">Artificial Flowers for Effortless Beauty — Imported, Durable, and Always Vibrant</h3>
Many people worry about the stress and cost of maintaining natural flowers: daily watering, trimming, 
and the inevitable ageing or fading of plants. This is why Farmgate Nigeria proudly introduces a 
stunning collection of premium artificial flowers, imported from the USA, Brazil, and China.
<h3 class="aboutHead"></h3>Our artificial flowers are:
<ul>
    <li>Vivid and bright all year round — they do not fade.</li>
    <li>Maintenance-free — no watering or trimming required.</li>
    <li>Perfectly structured — they retain their original shape, size, and colour.</li>
    <li>Ideal for homes, offices, events, and long-term decorations.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="aboutHead">Natural Flowers: Grown, Nurtured, and Maintained by Experts</h3>
For lovers of natural beauty, we also cultivate and supply high-quality live plants.
We plant, nurture, and maintain natural flowers to meet your exact preference.
<h3 class="aboutHead">Our specialties include:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Edge flowers: e.g. west-indian foreman and variegated ficus</li>
    <li>Lower-edge flowers: eg. begonia and rose periwinkle</li>
    <li>Spot flowers: eg. masqurede tree and christmass tree</li>
    <li>Aromatic flowers: eg. Queen of the night</li>
</ul>
Simply tell us your desired style or floral arrangement, and our team will deliver a refreshing, 
professionally designed transformation.
<h3 class="aboutHead">Years of Expertise in Landscaping & Floriculture</h3>

With extensive experience in floriculture and flower landscaping, Farmgate Nigeria offers unmatched 
value in plant propagation, garden design, and long-term flower maintenance. We maintain a rich selection
of natural flowers, including: West-Indian Foreman, Variegated Ficus and Plumbago Flower.
And in the rare case that your preferred flower runs out of stock, we will propagate and restock the 
exact quantity you need so you never miss your target.<br>
We also offer fumigation services to combat pests that commonly attack lawns and flower beds such as:
<ul>
    <li>Termites on gardens and carpet grass</li>
<li>Termites on cyca palm</li>
<li>Soldier ants on flower plots</li>
<li>Soldier ants around poultry areas</li>
<li>Other garden-related pest concerns</li>
</ul>
